        <abstract>
            <p>Comments favourably, though often differing, on articles by G. H. Lewes.</p> 
<p>Discusses claim of Agassiz [in <hi rend="italic">A journey in Brazil</hi> (1868)] that he found evidence of glaciers in Brazil. Suggests sponsoring an expedition to test these claims.</p> 
        </abstract>
